# 🛒 E-commerce Cart System

A simple e-commerce shopping cart system built with **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**. Users can browse products, add/remove items from their cart, and see the total amount before checking out.



## ✨ Features

- 🛍️ Product listings with name, image, and price  
- ➕ Add to Cart / ➖ Remove from Cart  
- 🧮 Quantity tracking and automatic subtotal/total calculation  
- 💾 Cart persists during session (can be extended with `localStorage`)  
- 🧾 Checkout button with placeholder logic (ready for Stripe integration)